    "title": "Mpango wa Wokovu wa Mungu Uliounganishwa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mpango wa wokovu wa mungu uliounganishwa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu anafunua mpango wake wa wokovu katika Maandiko. Hii ni mada kuu katika barua kwa Warumi. Katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21\">Warumi 3:21</a>, mtume Paulo anasisitiza mambo mawili muhimu kuhusu kuwa &quot;kufanywa kuwa wadilifu&quot; na Mungu kupitia Yesu Kristo:</p><ol><li><p>Haitaji kufuata sheria na kanuni za Agano la Kale.</p></li><li><p>Ilikuwa &quot;imeshuhudiwa na Sheria na Manabii&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21\">Warumi 3:21</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:2\">1:2</a>).</p></li></ol><p>Mungu daima alikusudia kuokoa dunia kupitia Yesu. Agano la Kale liliwaandaa watu kwa ajili ya wakati huu muhimu katika historia ya wokovu. Paulo mara nyingi anarejea kwenye mada hii ya mwendelezo wa maandiko (wazo kwamba ujumbe na matendo ya Mungu katika Biblia ni thabiti na yanaunganishwa katika Maandiko yote). Hii ni kweli hasa katika Warumi <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:1-Rom11:36\">9–11</a>. Hapo, Paulo anaeleza jinsi uhusiano wa Mungu na Israeli unavyofaa katika mpango huu unaoendelea.</p><p>Paulo anataka kutusaidia kuelewa mabadiliko katika mpango wa Mungu wa wokovu. Mpango huu unafunguka kwa hatua. Sasa kwa kuwa hatua ya mwisho katika Kristo imefika, hatua ya awali imekamilika. Sheria ya Mose haiwatawalii tena watu wa Mungu. Paulo mara nyingi anasisitiza kwamba uhusiano wetu mpya na Mungu ni tofauti na sheria ya Mose (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:14\">6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4-Rom7:6\">7:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:4\">10:4</a>).</p><p>Wazo kama hilo linaonekana katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:17\">Yohana 1:17</a> na <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1\">Waebrania 10:1</a>. Mtazamo wa Paulo katika Warumi kuhusu mpango wa Mungu unatusaidia kuelewa hadithi ya Biblia kwa njia inayoheshimu sehemu zote za mpango huu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21-Matt1:23\">Mathayo 1:21–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46-Luke1:55\">Luka 1:46–55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67-Luke1:79\">67–79</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10-Acts4:12\">Matendo 4:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34-Acts10:43\">10:34–43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:23-Acts13:41\">13:23–41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:3-Rom1:5\">Warumi 1:3–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16-Rom1:17\">16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21-Rom3:26\">3:21–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6-Rom5:11\">5:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:4\">8:1–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:5-Rom10:13\">10:5–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:26-Rom11:27\">11:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1-1Cor15:4\">1 Wakorintho 15:1–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:14-Gal2:21\">Wagalatia 2:14–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5-Gal3:14\">3:5–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:14\">Waefeso 1:3–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:22\">Wakolosai 1:15–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:3-1Tim2:6\">1 Timotheo 2:3–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9-2Tim1:10\">2 Timotheo 1:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27-Heb9:28\">Waebrania 9:27–28</a></p>",
